g with pipelines and storage at markham texas the cracker a  joint venture with mexichem that was constructed on time and on budget began commercial operations in  oxychem will use the ethylene to manufacture vinyl chloride monomer which mexichem will use to produce polyvinyl chloride pvc and pvc piping systems oxychem has been an active participant in the american chemistry councils responsible care® initiative since its inception in  demonstrating their commitment to attaining the highest levels of safety and environmental achievement responsible care companies implement worldclass management systems measure performance based on industrywide metrics and are subject to review by independent auditors oxychem is a fivetime winner of the american chemistry councils top safety performance award including the responsible care® company of the year award in  in recognition of outstanding achievements in environmental health safety and security performance eighteen oxychem facilities including the headquarters facility in dallas have achieved star status identifying them as among the safest work sites in the us under the occupational safety  health administrations osha voluntary protection program oxychems injury and illness incidence rate iir was  in  since  oxychem has achieved a  percent reduction of emissions of nitrogen oxides nox sulfur oxides sox carbon monoxide co particulate matter and volatile organic compounds “oxychem” is a registered trademark of occidental chemical corporation “oxyvinyls” is a registered trademark of occidental petroleum corporation“responsible care” is a registered service mark of american chemistry council incread oxychems statement pdf regarding its compliance with the california transparency in supply chains act of  find a product callout image  callout html  expand all  collapse all  basic chemicals chlorine and derivatives chlorine chlorinated organics methyl chloride methylene chloride chloroform carbon tetrachloride perchlorethylene e