dlargest merchant marketer in the world of chlorine and the largest marketer of its co‑product caustic soda chlorine is an essential building block in thousands of products that make our lives safer healthier and more convenient it plays a vital role in keeping the worlds water supplies safe by controlling harmful bacteria and viruses that can cause potentially deadly diseases such as typhoid and cholera approximately  percent of us public water treatment systems are chlorinebased chlorine is a key raw material in manufacturing pvc resins and more than  percent of all pharmaceuticals caustic soda has a wide variety of applications in many industries including pulp and paper aluminum soaps and detergents textiles petrochemicals and chemical processingoxychem is the world’s largest producer of caustic potash potassium hydroxide a principal component in fertilizers batteries soaps and detergents and specialty glasses the company also is the worlds largest producer of calcium chloride a premium salt with a variety of beneficial applications including ice control dust suppression road stabilization and oilfield servicesother products manufactured by oxychem have an array of key applications chlorinated organics serve as intermediates to make refrigerants among many other applications sodium silicates serve a wide range of enduse markets including silica products catalysts soaps and detergents paper products paint and pigments among many others chlorinated isocyanurates are sanitizers for residential swimming pools and spas  oxychem is the largest north american and only us producer of sodium chlorite which is used extensively in the water treatment industry for disinfection and purification find a product callout image  callout html  expand all  collapse all  basic chemicals chlorine and derivatives chlorine chlorinated organics methyl chloride methylene chloride chloroform carbon tetrachloride perchlorethylene ethylene dichloride edc dechlorane plus® hydrochloric acid h